OL,3,CPressure mounts on Welsh Government
OL,4,Cafter figures show rise in NHS waiting
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,FPressure is mounting on the new Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment after figures have revealed
OL,9,Fan increase in NHS waiting times since
OL,10,FPlaid Cymru won power.
OL,12,FIn May, around 542,600 patients were
OL,13,Fwaiting to be treated - up from around
OL,14,F536,500 in April.
OL,16,FProvisional data for June indicates
OL,17,Fanother increase in overall waits but
OL,18,Fa decrease in those over two years.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
