OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1784915311
OL,3,CPressure mounts on Welsh Government
OL,4,Cafter figures show rise in NHS waiting
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,FIt was the busiest June on record for
OL,8,FA&E attendances in Wales. The Welsh
OL,9,FAmbulance Service received more than
OL,10,F400 additional emergency calls a day.
OL,12,F63% of patients spent less than four
OL,13,Fhours in emergency departments - the
OL,14,Flowest figure on record and
OL,15,Fsignificantly below the 95% target.
OL,17,F11,826 patients waited 12 hours or
OL,18,Fmore - higher than in May and the
OL,19,Fsecond highest figure on record.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
