OL,3,CPressure mounts on Welsh Government
OL,4,Cafter figures show rise in NHS waiting
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,FPlaid Cymru won the Senedd election on
OL,8,F8 May and announced its cabinet five
OL,9,Fdays later, including a Minister for
OL,10,FHealth and Care, Deputy Minister for
OL,11,FPublic and Preventative Health, and
OL,12,FDeputy Minister for Social Care,
OL,13,FMental Health and Women's Health.
OL,15,FThe party has pledged to "do things
OL,16,Fdifferently" to tackle waiting times
OL,17,Fand improve NHS performance.
OL,19,FHealth and Care Minister Mabon ap
OL,20,FGwynfor described Thursday's figures
OL,21,Fas "disappointing and unacceptable".
OL,26,@wD@ZOUxD@LO]}D@DOU}D@cO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
