OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1784915311
OL,3,CPressure mounts on Welsh Government
OL,4,Cafter figures show rise in NHS waiting
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,F"Too many people are waiting for
OL,8,Ftreatment, and they are waiting too
OL,9,Flong. We have a plan to tackle this
OL,10,Fwhich will deliver the real change the
OL,11,Fpeople of Wales need to see and that
OL,12,Fthey rightly deserve," he said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@VO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
