OL,3,CPressure mounts on Welsh Government
OL,4,Cafter figures show rise in NHS waiting
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,FBut emergency medics branded the
OL,8,Fsituation a "shameful year-round
OL,9,Fcrisis".
OL,11,FDr Rob Perry from the Royal College of
OL,12,FEmergency Medicine (RCEM) said: "This
OL,13,Fis an unacceptable state of affairs,
OL,14,Fand some of the worst waiting times
OL,15,Fsince records began.
OL,17,F"The new Welsh Government has
OL,18,Fsignalled that it understands the need
OL,19,Fto reduce long waits and overcrowding,
OL,20,Fand we are pleased that it is engaging
OL,21,Fwith RCEM on this issue.
OL,26,@pD@MOUqD@GO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
