PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1784915311
OL,3,CPressure mounts on Welsh Government
OL,4,Cafter figures show rise in NHS waiting
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,F"I hope, for our patients' sake, that
OL,8,Fthese words become action soon. As
OL,9,Ftoday's figures show, the problem is
OL,10,Fonly going to get worse without the
OL,11,Fproper interventions."
OL,13,FThe Welsh NHS Confederation also said
OL,14,Fthe heatwave, coupled with pressures
OL,15,Fsuch as wildfires, put additional
OL,16,Fstrain on the health service.
OL,18,FDirector Darren Hughes said: "Despite
OL,19,Fthese challenges, NHS staff have
OL,20,Fworked tirelessly to respond to
OL,21,Fgrowing demand.
OL,26,@zD@^OU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
