OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1784915311
OL,3,CPressure mounts on Welsh Government
OL,4,Cafter figures show rise in NHS waiting
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,F"Targeted investment in measures such
OL,8,Fas improved ventilation and air
OL,9,Fconditioning in the NHS estate,
OL,10,Falongside additional capacity, would
OL,11,Fhelp make the NHS and key partners
OL,12,Fsuch as local government, more
OL,13,Fresilient to increasingly frequent
OL,14,Fextreme weather events."
OL,16,FLast month the Welsh Government
OL,17,Fappointed a group of experts to plan
OL,18,Fthe rollout of up to 10 surgical hubs
OL,19,Facross Wales - something Plaid Cymru
OL,20,Fpledged to do within 100 days of
OL,21,Fwinning power.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@XO]
